text: John Mills (3 June 1836 - 24 February 1899) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class match for New South Wales in 1857/58. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1836 births Category:1899 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Hampshire
title: John Mills (New South Wales cricketer)
